description:
This is a 44 minute workout called 'Extremely Powerful Guided Meditation to Manifest Your Dreams and Desires.' from the channel Rising Higher Meditation ®.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Create the life you wish to have and surrender your creation to the Infinite Intelligence.  Allow space for relaxation and ease while the universe takes care of it for you. EXTREMELY POWERFUL CREATION TOOL.
